    "description": "*ALL WARBAND &amp; COSMETIC DLC NOW INCLUDED IN THE MAIN GAME!*<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/29e1690e80172f0026af3aee9003d4ee.poster.avif?t=1760748580\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/29e1690e80172f0026af3aee9003d4ee.webm?t=1760748580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><i>Warhammer Underworlds – Shadespire Edition</i> is a digital adaptation of the explosive, high-stakes, turn-based strategy tabletop game from <strong>Games Workshop</strong> that pits mighty warbands from the <strong>Age of Sigmar</strong> universe against one another in an eternal player versus player battle for Glory. Choose a warband, build your decks and carve a path to victory using <strong>dice-and-card</strong> mechanics that offer boundless strategic depth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/af204ed5aa169586f445a359f28154a6.poster.avif?t=1760748580\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/af204ed5aa169586f445a359f28154a6.webm?t=1760748580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASSEMBLE YOUR WARBAND</h2>Trapped within the towering spires of the <strong>Mirrored City of Shadespire</strong>, fourteen warbands battle it out for survival - each with unique abilities and a distinct combat style. All of these warbands are now available to play in online matches, bot matches or single-player challenges, having previously been available as DLC! <br><br>Playable warbands:<br><br>Steelheart’s Champions - Magore's Fiends - Garrek’s Reavers - The Sepulchral Guard – Spiteclaw’s Swarm – The Farstriders – The Chosen Axes – Ironskull’s Boyz – Thorns of the Briar Queen – Eyes of the Nine – Drepur’s Wraithcreepers – The Storm of Celestus – Stormsire’s Cursebreakers – Mollog’s Mob<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/6f5caa630e05550d92b76cca1d246325.poster.avif?t=1760748580\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/6f5caa630e05550d92b76cca1d246325.webm?t=1760748580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT YOUR DECK</h2>Your success is measured in Glory points - awarded for achieving objectives and vanquishing your foes. <strong>Deckbuilding</strong> is the strategic heart of <i>Warhammer Underworlds – Shadespire Edition</i>. Your <strong>20-card power deck</strong> is filled with clever gambits, powerful upgrades, and cunning spells you’ll need to inflict maximum damage. Your<strong> 12-card objective deck</strong> will shape your tactical approach to a match, allowing you to score Glory by fulfilling specific conditions.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/e2b300bea7edae7f6d561e8234fc3447.poster.avif?t=1760748580\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1022310/extras/e2b300bea7edae7f6d561e8234fc3447.webm?t=1760748580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLAIM THE SPOILS OF SHADESPIRE</h2><br>A <strong>rewarding progression</strong> system in both online matches and single-player Challenges allows you to earn cosmetic content including warband skins, deck portraits, and player titles! Only those who have proven themselves in the unforgiving streets of Shadespire will be able to claim these rewards.",
